strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<se_def>*: Well, what have we here!? Customers, are ya?
<se_low>*: Greetings. I am a travelling priest. I'm actually still in training, but maybe there's something I can do to help you?
<se_def>*: If you keep going south along the path, you'll come to a town called Pickham. I wouldn't bother, though, if I were you.
<se_def>*: It's full of down-and-outs and thieves, you see. Everyone who has the misfortune to set foot in the place wishes they hadn't.
